    "With your generous financial assistance, I have great confidence in keeping WebServe healthy and maintaining it actively." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Dank Ihrer großzügigen finanziellen Unterstützung bin ich sehr zuversichtlich, WebServe gesund zu halten und aktiv weiterzuentwickeln."
          }
        },
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Grâce à votre généreux soutien financier, j’ai toute confiance dans le fait de garder WebServe en bonne santé et de le maintenir activement."
          }
        },
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "皆さまの惜しみないご支援のおかげで、WebServe を健全に保ち、積極的にメンテナンスし続ける自信があります。"
          }
        },
        "ko" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "여러분의 아낌없는 재정적 지원 덕분에 WebServe를 건강하게 유지하고 적극적으로 관리해 나갈 수 있다는 큰 자신감을 얻고 있습니다."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "有了你们慷慨的资助，我对保持 WebServe 的健康发展和积极维护它充满信心。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "有了您慷慨的資助，我更有信心讓 WebServe 保持良好狀態並持續積極維護。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Your generous financial assistance, I have great confidence in keeping WebServe healthy and maintaining it actively." : {
